# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:23
msgid "Quick Tutorial"
msgstr "Tutoriel rapide"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:25
msgid ""
"Using OpenShot is very easy, and this tutorial will take you through the "
"basics in **under 5 minutes**. After this tutorial, you will be able to make "
"a simple photo slide-show with music."
msgstr ""
"Utiliser OpenShot est très facile, et ce tutoriel vous guidera à travers les "
"bases en **moins de 5 minutes**. Après ce tutoriel, vous serez capable de "
"réaliser un simple diaporama photo avec musique."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:30
msgid "Basic Terminology"
msgstr "Terminologie de base"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:31
msgid ""
"To help understand the steps below, here are some definitions of a few basic "
"terms used in this tutorial."
msgstr ""
"Pour mieux comprendre les étapes ci-dessous, voici quelques définitions de "
"termes de base utilisés dans ce tutoriel."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:38
msgid "Term"
msgstr "Terme"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:38
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Description"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:40
msgid "Project"
msgstr "Projet"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:40
msgid ""
"A **project** includes references to all the video files and edits "
"(animations, titles, etc...), saved in a single file."
msgstr ""
"Un **projet** inclut les références à tous les fichiers vidéo et montages "
"(animations, titres, etc.), sauvegardés dans un seul fichier."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:41
msgid "Timeline"
msgstr "Timeline"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:41
msgid ""
"The **timeline** is an editing user interface that represents edits and "
"clips on a horizontal ruler. Time progresses from left to right."
msgstr ""
"La **timeline** est une interface de montage qui représente les montages et "
"clips sur une règle horizontale. Le temps s'écoule de gauche à droite."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:42
msgid "Track"
msgstr "Piste"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:42
msgid ""
"A separate **layer** on the timeline, which can hold clips. A timeline is "
"made up of many tracks, stacked vertically."
msgstr ""
"Une **couche** distincte sur la timeline, qui peut contenir des clips. Une "
"timeline est composée de plusieurs pistes empilées verticalement."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:43
msgid "Clip"
msgstr "Clip"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:43
msgid ""
"A **trimmed** portion of video, audio, or both positioned on a track, and at "
"a specific position in time. When files are dropped on the timeline, they "
"are represented as a Clip."
msgstr ""
"Une portion **découpée** de vidéo, audio, ou les deux, positionnée sur une "
"piste, à un moment précis. Lorsque des fichiers sont déposés sur la "
"timeline, ils sont représentés comme un clip."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:44
msgid "Transition"
msgstr "Transition"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:44
msgid ""
"A method to **blend** two images. Transitions can take many forms, including "
"cuts, dissolves, and wipes."
msgstr ""
"Une méthode pour **mélanger** deux images. Les transitions peuvent prendre "
"plusieurs formes, y compris les coupures, fondus enchaînés et volets."

